Key Match Events: Zach Edey and Jonas Valanciunas had to be separated and received double technical fouls at one point when things got too physical.
Post-Match Reflections: Zach Edey filled the stat sheet on Friday night with 3-pointers, blocks, rebounds and free throws.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Zach Edey came off the bench for the first time in his brief NBA career with 8:15 left in the first quarter.
Zach Edey scored 14 points, grabbed 8 rebounds, had 2 blocks, 2 steals, 2 assists, and shot 5-for-8 from the field, 1-for-2 from three-point range, and 3-for-3 from the free-throw line.
